### Phase E: Workflow Suggestion Toasts

After completing a process (e.g., a job finishes), show a toast in the lower-right suggesting the next logical step.

#### Flow Map:
```
Job complete → "Your list is verified! Launch an outreach campaign →"
Campaign created → "Connect your SMTP accounts for best results →"  
Domain health checked → "Review your send timing for this domain →"
Diff run → "Export your freshest contacts to a campaign →"
```

If the suggested feature requires a higher plan, clicking the toast opens the pricing modal instead.

